# artifacts/ holds mostly generated benchmark/sweep output (ignored).
# Only the curated deliverables below are tracked on purpose.
artifacts/*
!artifacts/submission.py
!artifacts/submission-check.py
!artifacts/submission_benchmark.json
!artifacts/kaggle_flow_0.png
!artifacts/kaggle_flow_1.png
!artifacts/kaggle_home.png
!artifacts/kaggle_signin.png
# Top-5 proxy opponent pool (public LB kernels) — tracked so the src zip ships a
# usable ruler; configs/eval_top5_proxy.yaml points here. Only top5_proxy is
# un-ignored; artifacts/opponents/producer* stays ignored.
!artifacts/opponents/
artifacts/opponents/*
!artifacts/opponents/top5_proxy/
# Ship only the runnable agent.py + README, not the source notebooks.
artifacts/opponents/top5_proxy/**/*.ipynb
# Non-pool kernels excluded from the ruler (torch+weights, or crash-prone — see
# top5_proxy README/memory). Present locally but NOT shipped: never loaded by the
# 6-agent pool, and exp48/i-m-stronger need weights that aren't bundled.
artifacts/opponents/top5_proxy/orbit-wars-exp48/
artifacts/opponents/top5_proxy/orbit-wars-i-m-stronger/
artifacts/opponents/top5_proxy/orbitbotnext/

